instructions: place Dinner Plate  on to the table in the center towards the closest edge
place the dinner fork directly to the left of the dinner plate
place the salad fork directly left of the dinner plate
place the dinner knife directly right of the dinner plate
place the salad knife directly left of the dinner knife
place the soup spoon directly to the right of the salad knife
pace the water glass directly 45 degrees to the right next to the dinner plate
place the wine glass directly to the right of the water glass
place another wine glass next to the one just placed down
place the coffee cup to the right of the soup spoon
place the bread plate 45 degrees to the left of the dinner plate
place the butter knife at a 45 degree angle on the top right of the bread knife
place the dessert fork horizontally above the dinner plate
place the dessert spoon horizontally above the dessert fork
place the napkin in the center of the dinner plate
